.SH NAME
mipi_dbi_pipe_update \- Display pipe update helper
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" mipi_dbi_pipe_update
.BI "(struct drm_simple_display_pipe *pipe "  ","
.BI "struct drm_plane_state *old_state "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "pipe" 12
Simple display pipe
.IP "old_state" 12
Old plane state
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
This function handles framebuffer flushing and vblank events. Drivers can use
this as their \fIdrm_simple_display_pipe_funcs->update\fP callback.
